metadata.title: Hungarian envoy calls on Deputy PM Ishaq Dar

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Apr 16 (APP): Ambassador of Hungary Bela Fazekas Wednesday called on Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister, Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar and discussed matters relating to mutual interests. During the meeting, they expressed keen interest in strengthening bilateral ties and looked forward to the upcoming visit of the Hungarian Minister of Foreign Affairs and Trade, Peter Szijjarto, a press release issued by the foreign office spokesperson said.
